Description: Distiller CM5 SDK - Self-contained Python SDK for hardware control
 The Distiller CM5 SDK provides a self-contained Python environment with modules,
 model files, and native libraries for audio, camera, e-ink display, and TTS/ASR
 on the CM5 platform.
 .
 This package installs to /opt/distiller-cm5-sdk and includes:
  * Python virtual environment with all dependencies
  * Python modules (distiller_cm5_sdk)
  * Model files for Whisper, Parakeet, Piper
  * Native shared library for e-ink display
  * All dependencies for hardware access and audio/video processing 
